nodes.text: Swift Return was a Consular-class cruiser that was destroyed by Admiral Trench prior to the Battle of Christophsis. At one point prior to its destruction, the Swift Return fired its weapons while in an asteroid field. When Galactic Republic Admiral Wullf Yularen researched Trench, believing the presumed-dead commander to be leading Separatist forces above Christophsis, he saw information on the Swift Return.
The Swift Return first appeared in a computer display in the Star Wars: The Clone Wars second season episode "Cat and Mouse".
